patthana8.74:1.1_0: Nasaraṇaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasaraṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … ekaṁ.
patthana8.74:2.1_0: Naaraṇaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naaraṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana8.74:3.1_0: Nasaraṇañca naaraṇañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nasaraṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … ekaṁ. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana8.74:4.1_1: ārammaṇe dve …pe… vipāke ekaṁ …pe… avigate pañca.
